%F A128899 T(n,k) = A039598(n-1,k-1) for n >= 1, k >= 1; T(n,0)=0^n.
%F A128899 T(n,k) = T(n-1,k-1) + 2*T(n-1,k) + T(n-1,k+1) for k >= 1, T(n,0)=0^n, T(n,k)=0 if k > n.
